    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who specialize in making guilloche designs, which are complex patterns or ornaments of interlaced curving bands, made by hand or with a specialized machine.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
